Achievements.Name: DEAD OR ALIVE 6 Master
Achievements.Description: Unlock all achievements.

Achievements.Name: Fighting Entertainment
Achievements.Description: Fight your debut battle (excluding training, offline player vs. player matches).

Achievements.Name: Change!
Achievements.Description: Change your main fighter.

Achievements.Name: Fledgling Fighter
Achievements.Description: Fight against computer in the VERSUS mode.

Achievements.Name: Cleared ARCADE course

Achievements.Name: Cleared TIME ATTACK course

Achievements.Name: Cleared SURVIVAL course
Achievements.Description: Clear a course in the SURVIVAL mode.

Achievements.Name: Exercise Newbie
Achievements.Description: Complete Command Training for a single character.

Achievements.Name: DOA Rookie

Achievements.Description: Buy a costume in the Wardrobe.

Achievements.Name: Records Keeper
Achievements.Description: Check the Fight Records.

Achievements.Name: The Observer
Achievements.Description: Watch a COM vs. COM battle in the Theater.

Achievements.Name: Learning From the Past
Achievements.Description: Watch a replay in the Theater.

Achievements.Name: Melomaniac
Achievements.Description: Purchase additional BGM.

Achievements.Name: DOApedia
Achievements.Description: Purchase DOA Encyclopedia in the Library.

Achievements.Name: Star Catcher
Achievements.Description: Collect one  during a quest.

Achievements.Name: Star Dust
Achievements.Description: Receive 10  in DOA QUEST mode.

Achievements.Name: Milky Way
Achievements.Description: Receive 100  in DOA QUEST mode.

Achievements.Name: Rival Rumble
Achievements.Description: Fight in your first ranked match.

Achievements.Name: Rival Deathmatch
Achievements.Description: Fight in 100 ranked matches.

Achievements.Name: Fighting For Real

Achievements.Name: The Hungry One

Achievements.Name: The Capable One

Achievements.Name: The Show-off
Achievements.Description: Win 5 consecutive Ranked Matches.

Achievements.Name: A Fight to Remember
Achievements.Description: Save a replay.

Achievements.Name: Rushing It
Achievements.Description: Win a match by executing a Fatal Rush attack (excluding offline PvP matches).

Achievements.Name: Smashing It
Achievements.Description: Win a match by executing a Break Blow attack (excluding offline PvP matches).

Achievements.Name: Grabbing It
Achievements.Description: Win a match by executing a Break Hold attack (excluding offline PvP matches).

Achievements.Name: No Escape!
Achievements.Description: Win a match by executing 3-hit combo after cancelling a Break Blow (excluding offline PvP matches).

Achievements.Name: I See Through It All
Achievements.Description: Win a match receiving 0 damage (offline player vs. player matches excluded).
